data.description: Welcome to 442 Fairgreen Ave! Introducing a captivating multi-level home set on a sprawling 1-acre parcel, offering the perfect blend of space, style, and serenity. This 4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom residence property presents and excellent opportunity to create lasting memories in a desirable setting. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances and ample counter space, while the inviting living areas are bathed in natural light. The expansive yard presents endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, from gardening to hosting gatherings.
